<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>The Cooperstown Diner</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fredoka+One&family=Righteous&family=Righteous:wght@400;700&family=Reem+Kufi:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
@keyframes flicker {
    0%, 19%, 21%, 23%, 25%, 54%, 56%, 100% { text-shadow: 0 0 10px #ff0000, 0 0 20px #ff0000, 0 0 30px #ff0000, 0 0 40px #ff0000; }
    20%, 24%, 55% { text-shadow: none; }
}

@keyframes slide-in {
    from { transform: translateX(-100%); opacity: 0; }
    to { transform: translateX(0); opacity: 1; }
}

*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Righteous',sans-serif;
}

html{
    scroll-behavior:smooth;
}

body{
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        45deg,
        #fef5e7,
        #fef5e7 10px,
        #f9f1d8 10px,
        #f9f1d8 20px
    );
    color:#8b0000;
}

header{
    position:fixed;
    width:100%;
    top:0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c41e3a 0%, #8b0000 100%);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    z-index:1000;
    border-bottom: 4px solid #ffd700;
}

.navbar{
    max-width:1200px;
    margin:auto;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
    padding:18px 25px;
}

.logo{
    font-size:2rem;
    font-weight:700;
    color:#ffd700;
    font-family:'Fredoka One',sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    animation: flicker 3s infinite;
}

.nav-links{
    display:flex;
    gap:35px;
    list-style:none;
}

.nav-links a{
    color:#fef5e7;
    text-decoration:none;
    transition:.3s;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    font-weight: 700;
    position: relative;
}

.nav-links a:hover{
    color:#ffd700;
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255,215,0,0.5);
}

.nav-links a::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -5px;
    left: 0;
    width: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: #ffd700;
    transition: width 0.3s;
}

.nav-links a:hover::after {
    width: 100%;
}

.hero{
    min-height:100vh;
    background:
    linear-gradient(rgba(139,0,0,.7),rgba(139,0,0,.7)),
    url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552566626-52f8b828add9?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80");
    background-size:cover;
    background-position:center;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    text-align:center;
    color:#fef5e7;
    padding:40px;
    position: relative;
}

.hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: 
        repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, transparent 2px, rgba(255,255,255,.03) 2px, rgba(255,255,255,.03) 4px);
    pointer-events: none;
}

.hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
}

.hero-content h1{
    font-size:4.5rem;
    margin-bottom:20px;
    font-family:'Fredoka One',sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-shadow: 3px 3px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), -1px -1px 0px rgba(255,215,0,0.3);
    animation: slide-in 0.8s ease-out;
}

.hero-content p{
    max-width:700px;
    margin:auto;
    font-size:1.2rem;
    line-height:1.8;
    font-family:'Reem Kufi',sans-serif;
    text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}

.buttons{
    margin-top:40px;
}

.btn{
    display:inline-block;
    margin:12px;
    padding:16px 35px;
    border-radius:0px;
    text-decoration:none;
    font-weight:800;
    transition:.3s;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    border: 3px solid;
    font-size: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 4px 4px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}

.btn-primary{
    background:#c41e3a;
    color:#fef5e7;
    border-color: #8b0000;
}

.btn-primary:hover {
    background: #8b0000;
    transform: translate(2px, 2px);
    box-shadow: 2px 2px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}

.btn-secondary{
    background:#ffd700;
    color:#8b0000;
    border-color: #cc9900;
}

.btn-secondary:hover {
    background: #ffed4e;
    transform: translate(2px, 2px);
    box-shadow: 2px 2px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}

.btn:hover{
    transform:translate(2px, 2px);
}

section{
    padding:90px 8%;
}

.section-title{
    text-align:center;
    margin-bottom:60px;
}

.section-title h2{
    font-size:3.2rem;
    font-family:'Fredoka One',sans-serif;
    color:#8b0000;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 0px rgba(255,215,0,0.4);
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    width: 100%;
}

.section-title h2::before,
.section-title h2::after {
    content: '★';
    margin: 0 20px;
    color: #ffd700;
}

.section-title p{
    color:#8b0000;
    font-family:'Reem Kufi',sans-serif;
    margin-top: 15px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
}

.features{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
    gap:25px;
}

.feature{
    background:#fef5e7;
    padding:35px;
    border-radius:0px;
    text-align:center;
    border: 4px solid #8b0000;
    box-shadow: 8px 8px 0px rgba(139,0,0,0.2);
    transition: all 0.3s;
    position: relative;
}

.feature::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -4px;
    left: -4px;
    right: -4px;
    bottom: -4px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd700, #ffed4e);
    z-index: -1;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
}

.feature:hover {
    transform: translate(-4px, -4px);
    box-shadow: 12px 12px 0px rgba(139,0,0,0.3);
    border-color: #c41e3a;
}

.feature h3{
    margin:15px 0;
    color:#8b0000;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
}

.feature p {
    font-family:'Reem Kufi',sans-serif;
    color: #333;
    font-weight: 600;
}

.menu-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));
    gap:30px;
}

.menu-card{
    background:#fef5e7;
    border-radius:0px;
    overflow:hidden;
    border: 5px solid #8b0000;
    box-shadow: 10px 10px 0px rgba(139,0,0,0.25);
    transition: all 0.3s;
    transform: rotate(0deg);
}

.menu-card:nth-child(2) {
    transform: rotate(-1deg);
}

.menu-card:nth-child(3) {
    transform: rotate(1deg);
}

.menu-card:hover {
    transform: rotate(0deg) translate(-5px, -5px);
    box-shadow: 15px 15px 0px rgba(139,0,0,0.3);
    border-color: #c41e3a;
}

.menu-card img{
    width:100%;
    height:220px;
    object-fit:cover;
    border-bottom: 4px solid #ffd700;
}

.menu-content{
    padding:25px;
}

.menu-content h3 {
    color: #8b0000;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.menu-content p {
    font-family:'Reem Kufi',sans-serif;
    color: #333;
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
}

.price{
    color:#c41e3a;
    font-weight:800;
    font-size:1.4rem;
    margin-top:15px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.story{
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b0000 0%, #c41e3a 100%);
    color:#fef5e7;
    text-align:center;
    border-top: 6px dashed #ffd700;
    border-bottom: 6px dashed #ffd700;
    position: relative;
}

.story::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 20px;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, #ffd700, #ffd700 10px, transparent 10px, transparent 20px);
}

.story h2{
    color:#ffd700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
}

.story p {
    font-family:'Reem Kufi',sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
}

.visit{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
    gap:40px;
}

.info-box{
    background:#fef5e7;
    padding:35px;
    border-radius:0px;
    border: 5px solid #8b0000;
    box-shadow: 10px 10px 0px rgba(139,0,0,0.2);
    transition: all 0.3s;
}

.info-box:hover {
    transform: translate(-5px, -5px);
    box-shadow: 15px 15px 0px rgba(139,0,0,0.3);
    border-color: #c41e3a;
}

.info-box h3{
    margin-bottom:20px;
    color:#8b0000;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.info-box p {
    font-family:'Reem Kufi',sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.info-box strong {
    color: #c41e3a;
}

footer{
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b0000 0%, #c41e3a 100%);
    color:#fef5e7;
    text-align:center;
    padding:50px 40px;
    border-top: 6px solid #ffd700;
    position: relative;
}

footer::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -15px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    background: #ffd700;
    border-radius: 50%;
}

footer h3{
    color:#ffd700;
    margin-bottom:15px;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
}

footer p {
    font-family:'Reem Kufi',sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 8px 0;
}

@media(max-width:768px){

.hero-content h1{
    font-size:2.5rem;
}

.nav-links{
    display:none;
}

.visit{
    grid-template-columns:1fr;
}

.section-title h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
}

.btn {
    margin: 8px;
    padding: 12px 25px;
}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="logo">The Cooperstown Diner</div>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="#menu">Menu</a></li>
            <li><a href="#story">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#visit">Visit</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>Breakfast & Lunch Since 1921</h1>
        <p>
            A Main Street original serving classic American diner food
            in the heart of Cooperstown, New York.
        </p>

        <div class="buttons">
            <a href="#menu" class="btn btn-primary">View Menu</a>
            <a href="tel:6072824367" class="btn btn-secondary">Call Takeout</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <div class="section-title">
        <h2>Why People Love Us</h2>
        <p>More than a century of great food and hospitality.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">
            <h3>🍳 Fresh Breakfast</h3>
            <p>Made fresh every morning.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature">
            <h3>🍔 Classic Burgers</h3>
            <p>American diner favorites.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature">
            <h3>⚾ Near Hall of Fame</h3>
            <p>Just steps away from baseball history.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature">
            <h3>👨‍👩‍👧 Family Friendly</h3>
            <p>Everyone feels at home here.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="menu">
    <div class="section-title">
        <h2>House Favorites</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="menu-grid">

        <div class="menu-card">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1568901346375-23c9450c58cd?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80">
            <div class="menu-content">
                <h3>Jumbo Burger Platter</h3>
                <p>Famous burger with lettuce, tomato and side.</p>
                <div class="price">$16.75</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-card">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1484723091739-30a097e8f929?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80">
            <div class="menu-content">
                <h3>Cinnamon Roll French Toast</h3>
                <p>Served with two eggs.</p>
                <div class="price">$12.00</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-card">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504674900247-0877df9cc836?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80">
            <div class="menu-content">
                <h3>Georgia Eggs</h3>
                <p>Homemade sausage gravy & cheddar.</p>
                <div class="price">$15.00</div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<section id="story" class="story">
    <div class="section-title">
        <h2>A Century on Main Street</h2>
    </div>

    <p style="max-width:800px;margin:auto;line-height:2;">
        Since 1921, The Cooperstown Diner has welcomed locals,
        families and visitors with classic comfort food and
        small-town hospitality. More than a restaurant, it's a
        Cooperstown tradition.
    </p>
</section>

<section id="visit">
    <div class="section-title">
        <h2>Visit Us</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="visit">

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>Location</h3>
            <p>136 1/2 Main St</p>
            <p>Cooperstown, NY 13326</p>
            <br>
            <p>📞 607-282-4367</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>Opening Hours</h3>
            <p>Sunday - Saturday</p>
            <p>7:00 AM – 2:00 PM</p>
            <br>
            <strong>Open Daily</strong>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<footer id="contact">
    <h3>The Cooperstown Diner</h3>
    <p>Real Food Since Day One.</p>
    <br>
    <p>136 1/2 Main St, Cooperstown, NY 13326</p>
    <p>607-282-4367</p>
    <br>
    <p>© 2026 The Cooperstown Diner</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
